                  ),
                ],
              ),
              child: Column(
                children: [
                  // Red header
                  Container(
                    width: double.infinity,
                    padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(
                        vertical: 16, horizontal: 20),
                    decoration: BoxDecoration(
                      color: AppTheme.dangerColor,
